parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the braking system at low speeds can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially when stopping or slowing down in heavy traffic, parking lots, or drive-thru lanes.
symptoms: Difficulty stopping or slowing down at low speeds
brake pedal feels soft or spongy
brake pedal is hard to press
vehicle rolls or slides before coming to a complete stop
vibration or stiffness in the brake pedal
"Service Trailer Brake System" or "Brake Assist" warning lights illuminate.

symptoms: Difficulty stopping or slowing down at low speeds
brake pedal feels soft or spongy
brake pedal is hard to press
vehicle rolls or slides before coming to a complete stop
vibration or stiffness in the brake pedal

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Defective wiring harnesses can cause the braking system to malfunction, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially when stopping or slowing down at low speeds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the trailer brake system can cause a distraction while driving, potentially leading to accidents, and may also prevent the trailer brakes from functioning properly, posing a risk to the driver and other road users.
symptoms: The "Service Trailer Brake System" warning message appears on the dashboard
accompanied by a loud
repetitive beeping noise
even when not towing a trailer. The warning message may persist for several minutes
blocking the speedometer and disabling Bluetooth features.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to shut off while driving, leading to a loss of power and control, which can result in accidents.
symptoms: Warning messages indicating that the forward collision system
StabiliTrak
and theft deterrent have failed
and other unknown messages are displayed. The vehicle may suddenly shut off
and the battery cable may need to be adjusted to restart the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the StabiliTrak system can cause the vehicle to lose traction and stability, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The "Service StabiliTrak" warning message appears on the dashboard
and the system may malfunction
causing the vehicle to lose traction and stability.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the infotainment system can cause a distraction while driving, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The radio/display screen constantly starts going haywire
scanning through stations
and changing stations
making it difficult to focus on driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the vehicle to lose power and control, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The power steering system fails
making it difficult to steer the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering assist can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn, making it hard to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The power steering assist warning light is illuminated
the steering wheel becomes difficult to turn
the vehicle loses power steering
the steering wheel has a lot of "play" in the turning of the wheel
the vehicle shuts down while driving
the steering wheel locks up
the vehicle is hard to maneuver.
